bomberman.core.logic
Class Strategy1

java.lang.Object
  bomberman.core.logic.Strategy1
All Implemented Interfaces:
MoveStrategy
public class Strategy1
extends java.lang.Object
implements MoveStrategy

The Strategy1 class is an implementation of the MoveStrategy interface. This strategy lets the DynamicPhysicsEntity move in a pseudo-random way around the FreeBlock ground, without moving on already visited blocks (when possible).

Author:
Federico Scozzafava
See Also:
MoveStrategy}, http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Strategy_pattern
